📘 Password Game

A browser-based puzzle game inspired by The Password Game, built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The goal is to create a password that satisfies a growing list of rules. Each new rule adds difficulty and often unexpected twists.

✨ Features

Interactive password input with dynamic rule validation
Rules displayed in real time as you progress
Clear feedback for each requirement (pass/fail)

🛠️ Tech Stack

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Deployment: GitHub Pages

